@Events_HostAddress = http://localhost:5119

# Use IDs from the ManifestTemplates.http and Venues.http runs, or replace with your own.
@venueId = 019e509a-17ba-759e-9650-afa6daf5dc89
@manifestTemplateId = 019e692a-bcd7-7307-990c-e5fb1dcf9e99

# After a successful CreateEvent call, paste the returned eventId here.
@eventId = 019e6a72-4951-7ef4-aeac-b6949a204e2d
@manifestId = 019e6a72-4952-7ebd-955d-25b75d754819

# Dev JWT: sub=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001, role=EventManager, exp=never
# Signed with the key in appsettings.Development.json — for local testing only.
# CreateEvent uses sub as AssignedManagerId; PublishEvent verifies caller matches.
@managerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIwMDAwMDAwMC0wMDAwLTAwMDAtMDAwMC0wMDAwMDAwMDAwMDEiLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRNYW5hZ2VyIiwiZXhwIjo5OTk5OTk5OTk5fQ.uY1m3u8JXwYtFOgijHhX4A7Iw3Fn7uT3uYntTwMPK8Q

### Create event - valid (with description)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "venueId": "{{venueId}}",
  "manifestTemplateId": "{{manifestTemplateId}}",
  "name": "Summer Concert 2026",
  "eventDate": "2026-08-15T19:00:00+00:00",
  "description": "Outdoor summer concert at the main arena."
}

### Create event - valid (no description)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "venueId": "{{venueId}}",
  "manifestTemplateId": "{{manifestTemplateId}}",
  "name": "Winter Gala",
  "eventDate": "2026-12-20T20:00:00+00:00",
  "description": null
}

### Create event - invalid (venue not found)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "venueId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "manifestTemplateId": "{{manifestTemplateId}}",
  "name": "Ghost Venue Event",
  "eventDate": "2026-09-01T18:00:00+00:00",
  "description": null
}

### Create event - invalid (manifest template not found)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "venueId": "{{venueId}}",
  "manifestTemplateId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "name": "Missing Template Event",
  "eventDate": "2026-09-01T18:00:00+00:00",
  "description": null
}

### Create event - invalid (event date in the past)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "venueId": "{{venueId}}",
  "manifestTemplateId": "{{manifestTemplateId}}",
  "name": "Past Event",
  "eventDate": "2020-01-01T00:00:00+00:00",
  "description": null
}

### Create event - invalid (name too long — over 200 chars)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "venueId": "{{venueId}}",
  "manifestTemplateId": "{{manifestTemplateId}}",
  "name": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA",
  "eventDate": "2026-09-01T18:00:00+00:00",
  "description": null
}

### Create event - invalid (empty name)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "venueId": "{{venueId}}",
  "manifestTemplateId": "{{manifestTemplateId}}",
  "name": "",
  "eventDate": "2026-09-01T18:00:00+00:00",
  "description": null
}

### Get event by ID (replace @eventId above with value from create response)
GET {{Events_HostAddress}}/events/{{eventId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get event - not found
GET {{Events_HostAddress}}/events/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

# ── Publish Event ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Requires: event created with the managerToken above (so AssignedManagerId matches sub).
# Paste the eventId returned from CreateEvent into @eventId at the top of this file.

### Publish event - valid (204 No Content)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events/{{eventId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### Publish event - not found (404)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### Publish event - wrong caller (403)
# Generate a different JWT (different sub) and use it here to test the 403 path.
# Example token: sub=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099, role=EventManager
@otherManagerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIwMDAwMDAwMC0wMDAwLTAwMDAtMDAwMC0wMDAwMDAwMDAwOTkiLCJyb2xlIjoiRXZlbnRNYW5hZ2VyIiwiZXhwIjo5OTk5OTk5OTk5fQ.udl5HS7LdTqKOL1LpL-ylSNET09oFYv7kxuinjFrXVQ
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events/{{eventId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{otherManagerToken}}

### Publish event - no token (401)
POST {{Events_HostAddress}}/events/{{eventId}}/publish
